{"tid":1130213,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[網戀L]就算幾夾係咪過唔到樣個關就完？","createTime":"2019-04-29T01:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T00:38:52.000Z","uid":186708,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf46c76c094969a3a420ced99397022c5130e4b","tid":1130213,"uid":186708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"我地情投意合 終於決定見面<br />\n但我好驚自己個樣嚇親佢<br />\n起碼我覺得見完 如果佢覺得失望 我地會少咗交流 感覺會唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a5d63f27ac12f16f801b8328e39ac007bd46bd","tid":1130213,"uid":18196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"相都冇睇過？"},{"pid":"7de42c5c848f635c169afdb069f97eea1c969d9d","tid":1130213,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"Do u feel right"},{"pid":"52c3cbe182620d70ed70dd5c5e6e0e2321dd33c4","tid":1130213,"uid":133436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"如果佢係暗瘡大肥婆 你咪又係冇哂feel<br />\n<br />\n咪咁痴線啦"},{"pid":"2f76606fb4abe89cd4fc8c5b81290226cbda63c9","tid":1130213,"uid":239565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"交換相先？"},{"pid":"e0e8fd81b77d2731f32649cb24069af3ac48f56f","tid":1130213,"uid":249306,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"你係想發展落去就始終有見面既一日架啦<br />\n之前同你有一樣諗法<br />\n雖然有交換過相 但怕出到黎會失望 <br />\n無論你或者對方都可能會<br />\n果時傾左3個月度 <br />\n驚時間拖得耐左對段關係冇好處 <br />\n所以最後都約左出黎<br />\n大家唔係靚仔靚女 但互相覺得順眼<br />\n第3次見面就正式一齊左 依家啱啱一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論係你不如諗下點執正自己 <br />\n乾淨冇口氣體味依啲基本野啦<br />\n第一次唔好亂咁同人有身體接觸 留個好印象<br />\n祝你好運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9212236e356cb2ceed9c5eb44cb06f673ed296","tid":1130213,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n張相靚仔過本人太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8304580d22a36da74b4c02366f721514a96799","tid":1130213,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"貨不對板 退貨好正常<br />\n落得ps裝甲呃人預左啦"},{"pid":"62e20dbc1c9b65886b187e8602a40090bc07306f","tid":1130213,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"第一印象好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果對方望到你順眼<br />\n有眼神contact 嘅話就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔要就冇下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6139b7d3cf678aa276e00e8b8ed648e25eddbb84","tid":1130213,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"冇相都出黎?"},{"pid":"8d96e0921d841cbd93436b72f406b68823863f1d","tid":1130213,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"戇鳩鳩<br />\n未見過點知夾唔夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e99dd1d2bd108b0aa771420c7c63e352ce3c8b","tid":1130213,"uid":200915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"見面如果唔合眼緣就會由夾都變唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}